{"tid":713912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【盜看世界盃】被捕21歲小網紅擁逾萬粉絲 為賺數千元面臨前途盡毀","createTime":"2018-06-23T08:28:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T08:31:48.000Z","uid":39464,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fdc3aeff7504cdce2314eedbb7396e2c19062231","tid":713912,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T08:28:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180623/large/1529730278_3abe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180623%2Flarge%2F1529730278_3abe.jpg&h=cb344b88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n海關首次破獲以手機Apps平台非法轉播世界盃賽事的案件，被捕的「小網紅」只有21歲，以「老公仔」的暱稱活躍於Voov手機直播平台Apps，其自我介紹寫著「NBA 英超 德甲 法甲 意甲 歐聯 歐霸盃 其他賽事」，故懷疑他早已涉嫌非法轉播過過其他球賽以吸引粉絲，他被捕前的粉絲(追隨者)總數多達1.3萬人，小網紅並累積收到49,810份禮物。若以官方「12.5個虛擬鑽石或金幣可兌換1元現金」推算，被捕小網紅至今最多也只不過能換取約4000港元收入，卻已因此面臨前途盡毀，因按《版權條例》相關侵權罪行最高可判監4年。<br />\n<br />\n海關消息人士則警告，涉嫌透過此直播平台盜看過世界盃的「老公仔」的粉絲，同樣涉嫌侵犯了世界盃賽事直播權持有人(now)的版權，根據《版權法例》版權持有人若查得盜嫌盜看者的身份，其實有權就其損失作出民事索償。故海關呼籲市民切勿參與非法盜看活動，免違法被追究。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180623/58354136\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180623%2F58354136&d=%2BbDes5M%2BhYKS2GX4MBi%2Bk%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=411b9f43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180623%2F58354136&h=bf8d30d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180623/58354136</a>"},{"pid":"318ad7486822833cb24ba22554bc8d1413b1cbd5","tid":713912,"uid":52358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T08:30:12.000Z","msg":"被捕小網紅至今最多也只不過能換取約4000港元收入<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啲大陸雞網紅一個鐘都唔止呢個數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded8b4a6acdf83c0842960f7bc21ae1835d3fdca","tid":713912,"uid":59373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T08:31:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d91e0e57f8cd0e393bd2307be697198eefa297bb","tid":713912,"uid":96486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"318ad7486822833cb24ba22554bc8d1413b1cbd5","tid":713912,"uid":52358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T08:30:12.000Z","msg":"被捕小網紅至今最多也只不過能換取約4000港元收入<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啲大陸雞網紅一個鐘都唔止呢個數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T08:31:48.000Z","msg":"有閪加波同冇既分別"}]}